                            <title>Prayer for all the days of the week</title>
                            <note>Possibly <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer">Prayer for the weekdays</ref> also attested elsewhere in the 
                                <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3985Mazmura">Mazmura Dǝngǝl</ref>, which cannot be determined as no images were available when this 
                                record was made.</note>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i6.1">
                                <locus from="56vb"/>
                                <title>Monday</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ዘሰኑይ፡ ኦእግዚእየ፡ ሔር፡ አምላክ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ወግሩም። ዘአልቦ፡ ጥንተ፡ ወኢተፍጻሜተ።</incipit>
                            </msItem>
